Klasse WinNT.TOKEN_INFORMATION_CLASS

java.lang.Object
com.sun.jna.platform.win32.WinNT.TOKEN_INFORMATION_CLASS
Umschließende Schnittstelle:
WinNT
public abstract static class WinNT.TOKEN_INFORMATION_CLASS extends Object
The TOKEN_INFORMATION_CLASS enumeration type contains values that specify the type of information being assigned to or retrieved from an access token.
